@page "/pathfinder-quiz"

<div class="quiz-header">
    <h1>Explore Career Possibilities</h1>
    <p>Take the 3 career quizzes to find out what occupations may be a good fit for you. These quizzes will help you identify possible career paths based on what you like or are good at.</p>
</div>

<div class="quiz-container">
    <!-- First Quiz Section -->
    <div class="quiz-card">
        <div class="quiz-status">
            <span>Not Completed</span>
        </div>
        <img src="/Interests.png" alt="Interests" />
        <h3>Interests</h3>
        <p>See where your interests lie, and explore what type of jobs would suit you well.</p>
        <a class="btn-quiz" href="/interests-quiz">Take the quiz</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Second Quiz Section -->
    <div class="quiz-card">
        <div class="quiz-status">
            <span>Not Completed</span>
        </div>
        <img src="/Abilities.png" alt="Abilities" />
        <h3>Abilities</h3>
        <p>Leverage your strengths. Find out what you are great at, and explore careers that allow you to use your top skills.</p>
        <a class="btn-quiz" href="/abilities-quiz">Take the quiz</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Third Quiz Section -->
    <div class="quiz-card">
        <div class="quiz-status">
            <span>Not Completed</span>
        </div>
        <img src="/WorkActivity.png" alt="Work Activities" />
        <h3>Work Activities</h3>
        <p>Choose how you prefer to work with data, people, and things, and get a list of possible career options to explore.</p>
        <a class="btn-quiz" href="/work-activities-quiz">Take the quiz</a>
    </div>
</div>

